WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.230 --> 00:00:03.320
Instead of checking the length of vViewPosition from the center of the view

00:00:03.320 --> 00:00:07.975
camera screen. Take the distance from vViewPosition to the uFlashOffset

00:00:07.975 --> 00:00:11.920
position. The distance function is built in and works for any type of vector,

00:00:11.920 --> 00:00:13.350
two, three or four elements.

